{"tid":1392384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講晒，贊唔贊成5/8 總動員文宣宣傳集會罷工，而唔係塞鐵強迫人罷？","createTime":"2019-07-31T17:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T08:46:25.000Z","uid":14715,"like":59,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"95173e888d263f13cd91490dddf205501d1640e2","tid":1392384,"uid":14715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 贊成<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔贊成<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得做文宣個觀感比塞鐵會好太多，塞鐵既話可能就算淺黃都會覺得反感，而且會比對家有機會做文章。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事實上的確好多人仲係覺得事不關己，你睇30/7 果日仲係大把人返工。我屋企人就係咁，口講就淺黃，但從來都無做過d 咩，文宣集會同罷工可以令件事更入屋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此外，法律風險會低好多，唔會令到好多人淆底而唔去參加/臨時縮沙， 做到李惠鈴講果個低成本高效益。 呢d 和理非野無必要做到咁吃力不討好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋其實好多人都想做文宣，但無材料，無人同自己做。<br />\n見到d 人係旺角天橋咁做，我諗好多人都願意，但可以有更好組織。<br />\n<br />\n我就希望係5/8 號當日或之前做個總動員出街文宣，宣傳返罷工同埋各區集會。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497bdc89af3bb728c0c4fe5dbf6782ec09680f1c","tid":1392384,"uid":14715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:24:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a918e2f3a78c1b62bdbd88fc18bb3eb469d1c5","tid":1392384,"uid":256105,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:40:00.000Z","msg":"請容許小弟講講本人既睇法<br />\n<br />\n人心、民意係長久致勝既重要因素<br />\n塞鐵塞巴士只會令一般中立或者淺黃慢慢反感<br />\n佢地心底知道政府黑警衰，但如果你長期影響到佢地日常生活，只會趕走佢地，令佢地反感，有d似雨傘後期，慢慢由理解變成厭煩，變成不關心<br />\n<br />\n所以我支持全力宣傳罷工，而非逼人被罷工"},{"pid":"991686e626e8864225438c087b93bef25c14beee","tid":1392384,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:42:36.000Z","msg":"要有6月嗰陣嘅文宣攻勢"},{"pid":"05f692355b5cf58b1801391e9b8e514acc264028","tid":1392384,"uid":290385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:42:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32b7455d468430bd5d832038cf83563da9de37d6","tid":1392384,"uid":111578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:43:58.000Z","msg":"其實both唔得咩"},{"pid":"50fad91130e6a4869a888bf004349411a3c9a1ec","tid":1392384,"uid":278168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:44:19.000Z","msg":"港豬唔係鍾意無得揀咩<br />\n咁維護一個逼人夾硬硬食嘅政權<br />\n咪俾佢硬食下囉"},{"pid":"b1e7873a9e5366f999a9fd4ab0717ba4bd5b8a9b","tid":1392384,"uid":14715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"50fad91130e6a4869a888bf004349411a3c9a1ec","tid":1392384,"uid":278168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:44:19.000Z","msg":"港豬唔係鍾意無得揀咩<br />\n咁維護一個逼人夾硬硬食嘅政權<br />\n咪俾佢硬食下囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:47:27.000Z","msg":"Marketing. <br />\n<br />\n你呢d 叫意氣用事。"},{"pid":"6c5720299b1e00352cf4ad5007a9cab55e11416f","tid":1392384,"uid":14715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f13a5e09c60b96c9bab87e8a4e7fcb9be22787e","tid":1392384,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:07:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bbb183c3bb82ba922851e65776bd7f6ee563c4f","tid":1392384,"uid":281232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:09:49.000Z","msg":"如果用強迫人罷工方法，有機會令到真心罷工嘅人，俾人當咗係因為俾人蓄意阻住先返唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e4c9c0346c9905d6c02d266f3cfa289fc9cd84","tid":1392384,"uid":263221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:09:54.000Z","msg":"why not both"},{"pid":"548edb79fa2d61fba946a8855a0d03c67b32b9aa","tid":1392384,"uid":77034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TboXRSK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTboXRSK.png&h=6259ad30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n會計界朋友、同事，請響應 5/8 請假、病假、罷工。<br />\n<br />\n多你一個就是多。<br />\n<br />\n[會計師] 5/8 工作安排 入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"42eeb1378a9da609826e54061c5741dee4a41851","tid":1392384,"uid":14715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92e4c9c0346c9905d6c02d266f3cfa289fc9cd84","tid":1392384,"uid":263221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:09:54.000Z","msg":"why not both"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:11:24.000Z","msg":"就係強迫人罷有問題先唔可以both.."},{"pid":"c2aaac6a03452ee3c660816e3c5b3e725aa5c6c9","tid":1392384,"uid":255437,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"92e4c9c0346c9905d6c02d266f3cfa289fc9cd84","tid":1392384,"uid":263221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:09:54.000Z","msg":"why not both"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:12:18.000Z","msg":"我哋爭取民主,但係我哋而家喺迫人哋罷工,自己諗"},{"pid":"5da8807a702f288d15c28f3a0fe47f9036a60bdc","tid":1392384,"uid":263221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:36:12.000Z","msg":"唔覺wo，7月30日等塞地鐵等左好耐都塞唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條路仲暢通過平時...<br />\n所以又真係會有人想不合作搞到佢地遲大到個wo<br />\n<br />\n罷工最主要既目的係想對社會經濟上有影響從而令政府回應，先唔討論一日係咪真係影響可以大到政府回應，但如果真係有人罷唔到(我覺得點都有人會係咁)，咁不合作可以令佢地遲幾粒鐘返工而令公司要停擺幾粒鐘，我覺得幾好wo，better than nothing ah ma<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba0bc2a6185999af2e1b9174b085bfebd887eff","tid":1392384,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:42:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f35b322f84059b3b260df69a40c4dff8134484b","tid":1392384,"uid":187950,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"03a918e2f3a78c1b62bdbd88fc18bb3eb469d1c5","tid":1392384,"uid":256105,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:40:00.000Z","msg":"請容許小弟講講本人既睇法<br />\n<br />\n人心、民意係長久致勝既重要因素<br />\n塞鐵塞巴士只會令一般中立或者淺黃慢慢反感<br />\n佢地心底知道政府黑警衰，但如果你長期影響到佢地日常生活，只會趕走佢地，令佢地反感，有d似雨傘後期，慢慢由理解變成厭煩，變成不關心<br />\n<br />\n所以我支持全力宣傳罷工，而非逼人被罷工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:46:46.000Z","msg":"既然我地爭取民主 就應該尊重返每個人既選擇 <br />\n既然d港豬 廢老乜柒都唔理掛住返工 迫他都冇意思"},{"pid":"d2e0363b13a8744eab1fb4060dd60d9e1e596c2a","tid":1392384,"uid":160166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:14:46.000Z","msg":"8/5 地鐵唔塞運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9dfac9eba1ee4701f27b3fb18b476e5f9297e039","tid":1392384,"uid":167467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:19:32.000Z","msg":"基督徒、天主教徒，想請你地幫個忙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392006</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fa9d0c627c1a94463e080ba38e49526793b73052","tid":1392384,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:46:25.000Z","msg":"宣傳緊"}]}